#

Classic Chicken Noodle Soup

45 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasyHearty

Description

A comforting bowl of chicken noodle soup, filled with tender chicken, hearty vegetables, and soft noodles, perfect for warming your soul.

Ingredients

  • chicken breast (boneless, skinless): 1 lb
  • egg noodles: 8 oz
  • carrots (sliced): 2
  • celery (sliced): 2 stalks
  • onion (chopped): 1
  • chicken broth: 6 cups
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • fresh parsley (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
